WEBVTT

01:57.039 --> 02:00.440
Your Majesty, an epidemic
has broken out in Huangpi Village.

02:00.760 --> 02:02.490
Dozens of people are infected.

02:02.640 --> 02:03.510
The situation

02:04.350 --> 02:05.430
doesn't look good.

02:06.000 --> 02:06.800
Open the door.

02:10.280 --> 02:12.150
How could you just leave us,

02:13.000 --> 02:15.750
abandoning me and your child?

02:27.240 --> 02:28.079
Make way.

02:28.800 --> 02:29.860
Careful, make way.

02:38.030 --> 02:38.910
Fei Zheng,

02:39.190 --> 02:40.850
what do you think we should do?

02:41.079 --> 02:41.960
Your Majesty,

02:42.030 --> 02:43.030
I believe

02:43.150 --> 02:45.680
we should send physicians
to Huangpi Village,

02:45.680 --> 02:47.000
set up quarantine areas,

02:47.000 --> 02:49.130
to prevent the spread of the epidemic.

02:49.150 --> 02:51.079
Meanwhile, we should
allocate food and medicine

02:51.079 --> 02:52.810
to meet the needs of the people.

02:53.190 --> 02:54.190
If necessary,

02:54.280 --> 02:55.590
we can ask the Eldest Princess

02:55.590 --> 02:57.560
to allocate funds from the treasury

02:57.560 --> 02:59.870
to support Huangpi Village
with all available resources.

02:59.870 --> 03:00.520
Good.

03:00.710 --> 03:01.520
Let's do it.

03:01.800 --> 03:02.600
Your Majesty,

03:03.470 --> 03:05.630
Lord Fei makes it sound easy,

03:05.870 --> 03:08.470
but it won't be so simple in practice.

03:08.590 --> 03:09.680
Lord Fei said

03:09.680 --> 03:11.840
to send physicians
to Huangpi Village.

03:11.840 --> 03:13.680
If they get infected,

03:13.870 --> 03:15.470
who will treat them?

03:15.800 --> 03:17.150
He also said

03:17.150 --> 03:18.750
to set up quarantine areas.

03:18.750 --> 03:20.870
If all infected people go there,

03:20.870 --> 03:23.400
who will take care of their daily needs?

03:23.400 --> 03:25.360
Are we leaving them to die?

03:25.470 --> 03:27.870
We need to transport food and medicine.

03:28.030 --> 03:29.870
If infection occurs during transport,

03:29.870 --> 03:33.190
wouldn't it harm more innocent people?

03:33.190 --> 03:34.190
Furthermore,

03:34.360 --> 03:35.840
are the treasury funds

03:35.840 --> 03:38.030
meant for commoners to use?

03:38.030 --> 03:39.630
Lord Li makes sense.

03:39.630 --> 03:40.680
If the physicians get sick,

03:40.680 --> 03:41.840
it will indeed be troublesome.

03:41.840 --> 03:42.590
Yes.

03:42.910 --> 03:44.870
If the disease spreads to the capital,

03:44.870 --> 03:46.520
the consequences will be unimaginable.

03:46.520 --> 03:47.590
Lord Fei

03:47.590 --> 03:49.280
is still too young.

03:49.430 --> 03:51.090
You all are absolutely right.

03:51.630 --> 03:54.470
I'm sure Lord Li has a brilliant idea.

03:54.680 --> 03:55.960
Why not speak up

03:55.960 --> 03:57.470
and enlighten us

03:57.470 --> 03:58.800
so we may learn from you?

04:02.400 --> 04:03.280
Your Majesty,

04:03.630 --> 04:04.800
the epidemic is spreading.

04:04.800 --> 04:06.590
If we don't take decisive measures

04:06.590 --> 04:08.360
and allow it to worsen,

04:08.360 --> 04:09.840
not only the capital

04:10.080 --> 04:11.630
but all of Jinglan

04:12.030 --> 04:15.280
will fall into an abyss of no return.

04:15.630 --> 04:16.480
Lord Zhang,

04:17.269 --> 04:18.560
what kind of

04:19.070 --> 04:20.510
decisive measures

04:20.800 --> 04:22.060
are you talking about?

04:24.480 --> 04:25.280
Your Majesty,

04:25.600 --> 04:27.430
to save the people of Jinglan,

04:27.430 --> 04:28.830
we must act decisively.

04:28.830 --> 04:31.560
If necessary, we must
abandon Huangpi Village.

04:34.480 --> 04:35.280
Your Majesty,

04:35.830 --> 04:38.690
I believe this method
is absolutely unacceptable.

04:38.750 --> 04:39.870
The people are innocent.

04:39.870 --> 04:41.750
We should do our best to treat them.

04:41.750 --> 04:43.150
We cannot give up easily.

04:43.360 --> 04:44.159
Xiao Chi.

04:44.830 --> 04:47.560
You have killed so many
enemies on the battlefield.

04:47.560 --> 04:48.870
Why are you

04:48.870 --> 04:50.800
being soft-hearted at this time?

04:50.920 --> 04:52.120
The ones I killed on the battlefield

04:52.120 --> 04:53.480
were enemies.

04:53.750 --> 04:54.870
And those you are going to abandon

04:54.870 --> 04:56.560
are the people of Jinglan.

04:56.560 --> 04:59.560
It is for the sake of more people

04:59.600 --> 05:02.270
that I abandon a small Huangpi Village.

05:02.720 --> 05:03.430
We,

05:03.630 --> 05:04.830
all of us here,

05:05.270 --> 05:08.600
are people who have experienced
the disaster 8 years ago.

05:08.600 --> 05:09.630
At that time,

05:09.630 --> 05:12.240
it was because we were soft-hearted

05:12.240 --> 05:14.430
that the people of the whole Jinglan

05:14.430 --> 05:16.190
suffered terribly.

05:16.560 --> 05:17.480
At that time,

05:17.480 --> 05:19.680
you and Lord Fei were still young.

05:20.750 --> 05:23.070
His Majesty was also young.

05:23.480 --> 05:25.560
It's understandable that you forget

05:26.070 --> 05:27.830
about this matter quickly.

05:28.190 --> 05:29.000
Lord Zhang.

05:29.680 --> 05:31.160
We were ignorant at that time.

05:31.160 --> 05:31.950
Now,

05:32.240 --> 05:34.440
we can definitely solve this epidemic.

05:35.270 --> 05:36.480
Okay.

05:37.360 --> 05:38.680
Then General Xiao,

05:39.070 --> 05:41.600
you will be personally
responsible for this.

05:41.830 --> 05:43.000
Do you dare to go?

05:43.430 --> 05:44.120
Of course.

05:47.070 --> 05:47.870
Your Majesty,

05:47.870 --> 05:50.040
I am willing to go with General Xiao.

05:50.750 --> 05:51.560
Xiao Chi.

05:52.159 --> 05:52.950
The epidemic in Huangpi Village

05:52.950 --> 05:54.070
is serious.

05:55.070 --> 05:55.830
Are you

05:57.560 --> 05:58.630
really going?

05:59.390 --> 06:00.240
Your Majesty,

06:00.360 --> 06:01.270
human effort can achieve anything.

06:01.270 --> 06:03.510
I will definitely not let
the tragedy of 8 years ago

06:03.510 --> 06:04.480
happen again.

06:04.950 --> 06:05.750
Fei Zheng,

06:06.630 --> 06:08.160
stay by my side

06:08.680 --> 06:09.830
and be on standby.

06:11.190 --> 06:12.000
Xiao Chi.

06:12.830 --> 06:13.950
You must be very careful

06:13.950 --> 06:15.160
this time when you go

06:15.480 --> 06:16.540
to Huangpi Village

06:17.040 --> 06:18.360
to save the people.

06:18.630 --> 06:19.160
Yes.

06:20.120 --> 06:22.520
It's fine if the disease
can be controlled.

06:23.360 --> 06:25.070
If it can't be controlled...

06:27.800 --> 06:28.680
Lord Zhang,

06:29.390 --> 06:30.560
what do you think?

06:30.830 --> 06:32.760
Your Majesty has already decided.

06:33.070 --> 06:33.830
I

06:34.600 --> 06:35.659
have no objection.

06:36.120 --> 06:36.950
Alright.

06:39.070 --> 06:40.730
Xiao Chi, receive the decree.

06:41.270 --> 06:42.070
I obey.

06:43.159 --> 06:44.600
If you go to Huangbei Village

06:44.600 --> 06:45.830
to aid the people

06:46.600 --> 06:48.270
and return victorious,

06:48.950 --> 06:51.240
I shall elevate you
as a pillar of the state.

06:51.240 --> 06:52.370
I accept the decree,

06:52.510 --> 06:54.360
and will definitely
not fail Your Majesty's trust

06:54.360 --> 06:56.159
and the people's expectations.

06:58.950 --> 06:59.800
Xiao Chi?

07:00.750 --> 07:01.560
You're awake.

07:03.240 --> 07:04.190
You were

07:04.750 --> 07:05.750
asleep just now,

07:05.750 --> 07:07.550
so I didn't go in and disturb you.

07:08.480 --> 07:10.240
You're looking for me
about Huangpi Village, right?

07:10.240 --> 07:11.040
That's right.

07:11.070 --> 07:13.160
The situation in Huangpi Village
is very serious this time.

07:13.160 --> 07:14.680
So I cannot stay out of it.

07:14.680 --> 07:15.430
I know.

07:16.040 --> 07:17.430
But if you get infected,

07:17.430 --> 07:17.830
you...

07:22.680 --> 07:24.410
Everyone will worry about you.

07:27.830 --> 07:29.030
I know what I'm doing.

07:29.240 --> 07:31.240
Healing the sick is my bounden duty.

07:31.390 --> 07:33.680
I can't back down just because
I'm afraid of getting infected.

07:33.680 --> 07:35.390
I have never doubted your medical skills.

07:35.390 --> 07:37.000
But this time is truly different.

07:37.000 --> 07:38.430
If I don't go,

07:38.480 --> 07:40.360
do you have a better candidate?

07:50.870 --> 07:52.360
We'll face this together.

07:55.270 --> 07:56.070
Alright.

07:56.600 --> 07:57.480
But promise me,

07:57.800 --> 07:59.330
you must not act on your own.

08:00.190 --> 08:01.000
When it comes to treating the illness,

08:01.000 --> 08:01.870
I am in charge,

08:01.950 --> 08:03.680
and you must cooperate with me.

08:03.830 --> 08:04.630
Alright,

08:05.270 --> 08:06.270
I will cooperate.

08:06.870 --> 08:08.560
By the grace of Heaven,

08:08.560 --> 08:10.070
the Emperor proclaims:

08:10.070 --> 08:11.810
An epidemic has broken out
in Huangpi Village,

08:11.810 --> 08:13.560
and the people are in danger.

08:13.560 --> 08:16.390
I heard Physician Han
is well-versed in pharmacology.

08:16.390 --> 08:19.870
The Imperial Medical Academy
is ordered to follow her command,

08:19.870 --> 08:22.630
and assist in the dispatch
of all medical supplies.

08:22.630 --> 08:24.160
Make no mistake.

08:24.160 --> 08:24.950
So ordered.

08:24.950 --> 08:25.680
Let me test you.

08:25.680 --> 08:26.750
What is this?

08:26.750 --> 08:27.870
This is Angelica.

08:27.870 --> 08:28.630
Mmm.

08:28.830 --> 08:29.600
Yunling.

08:29.870 --> 08:31.360
Even though you are a girl,

08:31.720 --> 08:33.030
I want you to become

08:33.030 --> 08:35.750
a physician who can
treat the common people,

08:35.840 --> 08:38.480
with a benevolent heart and skilled hands.

08:39.240 --> 08:41.320
I will definitely not
let you down, Father.

08:41.320 --> 08:42.480
Mmm.

09:21.440 --> 09:22.240
Mo.

09:23.080 --> 09:24.880
Your injuries have healed a lot.

09:25.150 --> 09:27.680
It seems Liu Xiyang
has taken good care of you.

09:29.870 --> 09:30.870
Tomorrow,

09:31.550 --> 09:33.030
I have to go out with Xiao Chi

09:33.030 --> 09:34.960
to handle some important matters.

09:35.840 --> 09:38.500
I won't be able to visit you
for the next few days.

09:46.270 --> 09:47.080
Mo.

09:47.840 --> 09:49.240
Wake up soon.

09:50.670 --> 09:53.240
If Uncle Lie knew you were still alive,

09:53.670 --> 09:55.200
how happy he would be!

09:59.080 --> 10:01.080
As long as I come back safely,

10:01.630 --> 10:04.160
I will definitely save you
and bring you back.

10:12.480 --> 10:15.080
The medicines and necessities
have been loaded onto the carts.

10:15.080 --> 10:16.360
Good. Thank you.

10:19.870 --> 10:21.200
General Xiao.

10:27.030 --> 10:27.870
Lord Zhang.

10:33.000 --> 10:34.030
General Xiao.

10:34.790 --> 10:37.030
You're about to leave for Huangpi Village.

10:37.030 --> 10:37.960
I have

10:38.270 --> 10:40.630
specially prepared a gift for you.

10:40.840 --> 10:41.630
A gift?

10:46.840 --> 10:48.600
This is a token of my regard.

10:48.600 --> 10:51.200
I wish you a speedy victory,

10:51.270 --> 10:52.670
a safe return,

10:52.670 --> 10:54.750
and promotion with wealth.

10:54.790 --> 10:56.240
I accept your

10:56.600 --> 10:57.600
kind intentions.

10:58.030 --> 10:59.120
I won't

10:59.120 --> 11:01.550
fail to live up to your expectations.

11:01.870 --> 11:02.870
That's good.

11:03.630 --> 11:04.790
I hope the two of you

11:05.000 --> 11:06.480
look out for yourselves.

11:07.030 --> 11:08.090
I won't see you out.

11:08.670 --> 11:09.480
Humph.

11:14.000 --> 11:15.330
You can put up with that?

11:15.360 --> 11:16.160
It's nothing.

11:16.440 --> 11:17.550
At Tianlang Pass,

11:17.750 --> 11:19.150
I've seen plenty of this.

11:19.840 --> 11:20.630
Xiao Chi.

11:22.030 --> 11:23.480
The epidemic in Huangpi Village

11:23.480 --> 11:24.390
is no joke.

11:25.270 --> 11:25.870
You two must

11:25.870 --> 11:27.870
prioritize your own safety
above everything else.

11:27.870 --> 11:29.200
Don't push yourselves.

11:29.550 --> 11:30.750
Rest assured, Zheng.

11:31.480 --> 11:32.030
Let's go.

11:32.030 --> 11:32.600
Okay.

11:57.120 --> 11:57.960
I didn't expect

11:57.960 --> 11:59.150
it to be so serious.

12:00.790 --> 12:01.600
Sir!

12:02.000 --> 12:02.720
Sir!

12:02.720 --> 12:03.670
Please open the door!

12:03.670 --> 12:05.000
Save my child!

12:05.670 --> 12:06.480
Sir!

12:06.480 --> 12:07.670
Save my child!

12:07.670 --> 12:08.390
Open it.

12:08.720 --> 12:10.030
Save my child!

12:11.670 --> 12:14.390
Sir, please save my child!

12:14.390 --> 12:16.030
He's dying.

12:16.600 --> 12:18.240
He's dying!

12:18.240 --> 12:19.840
The child is already dead.

12:20.960 --> 12:21.480
No!

12:22.840 --> 12:24.030
This isn't real.

12:24.030 --> 12:24.960
My condolences.

12:25.120 --> 12:26.440
You're lying to me.

12:27.550 --> 12:28.360
Are you okay?

12:28.960 --> 12:30.670
You're lying to me!

12:36.790 --> 12:38.670
Let's go in and check on the others first.

12:38.670 --> 12:39.440
After going in,

12:39.440 --> 12:41.000
make sure to protect yourself.

12:41.000 --> 12:42.240
My child!

12:53.030 --> 12:54.390
Has the court just given up on us?

12:54.390 --> 12:56.150
Are they leaving us to die?

12:56.150 --> 12:56.750
Yeah! Yeah!

12:56.750 --> 12:57.670
We are just...

12:58.440 --> 12:59.270
Just what?

12:59.270 --> 12:59.910
We're just nobodies

12:59.910 --> 13:01.390
from a small place like Huangpi Village.

13:01.390 --> 13:02.480
If we die,

13:02.480 --> 13:03.240
who will care?

13:03.240 --> 13:04.120
Who will care?

13:04.390 --> 13:05.000
Right!

13:05.670 --> 13:07.000
Don't worry, everyone.

13:07.390 --> 13:08.080
His Majesty

13:08.600 --> 13:10.860
will not abandon any subject of Jinglan.

13:11.390 --> 13:13.080
General Xiao, you're finally here.

13:13.080 --> 13:14.240
This is General Xiao.

13:14.240 --> 13:16.150
Folks, we are saved!

13:16.670 --> 13:17.870
Don't worry, everyone.

13:17.870 --> 13:19.390
We will do our best

13:19.480 --> 13:20.960
to help everyone get out of danger.

13:20.960 --> 13:21.760
General Xiao,

13:21.840 --> 13:22.630
I believe in you.

13:22.630 --> 13:23.630
We believe in you.

13:23.630 --> 13:25.630
We believe in you!

13:25.630 --> 13:27.080
We believe in you!

13:28.030 --> 13:29.870
Everyone, come and get your medicine.

13:29.870 --> 13:31.630
Please cooperate with
the physicians' treatment,

13:31.630 --> 13:32.750
to contain the disease
as soon as possible.

13:32.750 --> 13:34.080
Line up!

13:34.270 --> 13:35.240
Great!

13:35.240 --> 13:36.870
Line up!

13:39.240 --> 13:40.550
Thank you, Sir.

13:40.550 --> 13:41.360
Thank you.

13:42.480 --> 13:43.010
General.

13:43.240 --> 13:44.200
I am Chen Yuan,

13:44.480 --> 13:46.670
the physician
in charge of Huangpi Village.

13:46.670 --> 13:47.550
This is...

13:47.910 --> 13:48.640
Han Yunling,

13:49.000 --> 13:51.200
a physician who came
with me from the border.

13:51.200 --> 13:53.200
Tell her about the current situation.

13:53.200 --> 13:53.840
Yes.

13:54.360 --> 13:55.270
In the past few days,

13:55.270 --> 13:56.480
I've gone through the medical texts,

13:56.480 --> 13:57.790
and found that these symptoms

13:57.790 --> 13:59.790
closely resemble the Death Plague.

14:00.030 --> 14:01.030
But for the so-called Death Plague,

14:01.030 --> 14:03.480
there are no recorded cases
of successful treatment.

14:03.480 --> 14:04.480
I really

14:04.750 --> 14:06.360
have no idea what to do.

14:06.670 --> 14:07.750
According to the records

14:07.750 --> 14:09.600
in Uncle Lie's notes, Death Plague

14:09.600 --> 14:11.000
is transmissible among humans.

14:11.000 --> 14:12.360
We should find a clean place

14:12.360 --> 14:13.600
to serve as a specialized
treatment facility,

14:13.600 --> 14:15.840
and treat all
the infected patients in isolation

14:15.840 --> 14:16.630
to prevent future trouble.

14:16.630 --> 14:17.750
Is there a cure?

14:18.240 --> 14:19.870
Although there are
ancient prescriptions in the notes,

14:19.870 --> 14:21.030
whether they are feasible

14:21.030 --> 14:22.090
remains to be seen.

14:22.390 --> 14:23.480
In that case,

14:23.750 --> 14:24.840
separate the patients

14:24.840 --> 14:25.870
from the others

14:26.030 --> 14:26.670
and treat them in isolation.

14:26.670 --> 14:28.270
Everyone inside is sick.

14:28.480 --> 14:30.480
Won't we get infected if we go in?

14:30.480 --> 14:32.240
Exactly. No way.

14:32.240 --> 14:33.440
My family has had only
1 son for 3 generations.

14:33.440 --> 14:34.870
Whoever wants to go can go.

14:34.870 --> 14:36.840
I know you are all afraid,

14:37.000 --> 14:38.670
but they are our family.

14:38.750 --> 14:40.670
They need us the most right now.

14:40.870 --> 14:42.030
Please rest assured,

14:42.030 --> 14:43.320
I will go in with you.

14:43.320 --> 14:44.080
Who are you?

14:44.080 --> 14:45.440
Why should I trust you?

14:45.480 --> 14:46.360
Exactly.

14:46.360 --> 14:47.030
A little girl

14:47.030 --> 14:48.750
pretending to be a military doctor.

14:48.750 --> 14:49.810
Listen, everyone.

14:49.960 --> 14:52.030
Isn't this little girl
just messing around?

14:52.030 --> 14:52.790
Right.

14:53.000 --> 14:53.790
Exactly.

14:53.790 --> 14:55.670
Physician Han was sent by His Majesty.

14:55.670 --> 14:56.930
If you don't trust her,

14:57.120 --> 14:58.480
do you not trust His Majesty?

14:58.480 --> 14:59.390
General Xiao.

14:59.870 --> 15:01.000
Can this little girl

15:01.000 --> 15:03.000
really cure that darn Death Plague?

15:03.480 --> 15:05.200
Although Death Plague is dangerous,

15:05.200 --> 15:06.720
it's not incurable.

15:07.030 --> 15:07.480
Physician Han

15:07.480 --> 15:09.410
will do her best to treat everyone.

15:09.480 --> 15:10.680
Please rest assured.

15:11.080 --> 15:12.030
Physician Han.

15:15.030 --> 15:17.960
My sister and I want to
help at the quarantine center.

15:17.960 --> 15:18.750
Sure.

15:19.670 --> 15:21.840
But what about the adults
from your family?

15:21.840 --> 15:23.150
We don't have any.

15:24.120 --> 15:25.240
They are sisters.

15:25.240 --> 15:26.270
The older one is Cuizhi,

15:26.270 --> 15:27.750
and the younger one is Cuimiao.

15:27.750 --> 15:28.790
Their parents

15:28.790 --> 15:30.030
also got Death Plague

15:30.150 --> 15:32.320
and died the day before yesterday.

15:34.600 --> 15:36.200
Then both of you come and help,

15:36.200 --> 15:36.840
okay?

15:38.080 --> 15:38.870
Okay.

15:39.360 --> 15:41.550
General Xiao has fought for years
to defend the country.

15:41.550 --> 15:42.960
I trust you. I'll go.

15:43.270 --> 15:44.080
I'll go too.

15:46.240 --> 15:47.240
We'll go too.

15:48.840 --> 15:49.970
You must be careful.

15:52.750 --> 15:53.870
The medicine is here.

15:53.870 --> 15:54.550
The water is here.

15:54.550 --> 15:56.150
Quick, bring the medicine.

15:56.150 --> 15:56.630
Over here.

15:56.630 --> 15:59.840
Coming.

15:59.840 --> 16:00.670
Careful, it's hot.

16:00.670 --> 16:01.240
Go get some water.

16:01.240 --> 16:02.080
Bring another basin of water.

16:02.080 --> 16:03.670
Someone is coughing up blood inside again.

16:03.670 --> 16:06.870
Coming.

16:08.960 --> 16:09.750
How is it?

16:09.750 --> 16:11.280
Everything is fine for now.

16:18.480 --> 16:20.840
Physician Han, this patient is dying.

16:21.150 --> 16:22.610
Please go and check on him.

16:31.000 --> 16:32.200
Come and check on him.

16:33.360 --> 16:34.790
Go get Physician Han.

16:35.390 --> 16:36.630
Physician Han.

16:36.630 --> 16:37.550
This patient is dying.

16:37.550 --> 16:38.840
Come and check on him.

16:39.870 --> 16:40.840
Let me see.

17:17.030 --> 17:18.829
I am willing to sacrifice my life

17:19.480 --> 17:21.740
to end this disaster in Huangpi Village.

17:25.680 --> 17:27.349
Thank you.

17:30.720 --> 17:31.640
Thank you, Sir.

17:34.000 --> 17:35.240
Thank you.

17:35.240 --> 17:36.240
Thank you.

17:37.830 --> 17:40.400
How is the situation with Xiao Chi?

17:41.200 --> 17:42.680
There is no news yet.

17:42.830 --> 17:44.550
So many days have passed.

17:45.350 --> 17:47.590
Why is there no news at all?

17:48.160 --> 17:48.960
Your Majesty,

17:49.350 --> 17:51.030
I came to see you today

17:51.030 --> 17:53.630
to ask for permission
to go to Huangpi Village.

17:55.640 --> 17:56.480
Okay.

17:57.440 --> 17:58.000
Then,

17:59.240 --> 18:00.160
take care.

18:03.030 --> 18:04.550
Don't go empty-handed.

18:05.880 --> 18:07.160
Xie, why are you here?

18:08.400 --> 18:09.260
Your Highness.

18:09.510 --> 18:10.750
As the Eldest Princess,

18:10.750 --> 18:11.680
how could I stand by and do nothing

18:11.680 --> 18:13.680
with the situation in Huangpi Village?

18:13.680 --> 18:16.540
I have ordered people
to prepare food and medicine,

18:16.640 --> 18:18.040
as well as Atractylodes.

18:18.160 --> 18:20.590
I heard that burning Atractylodes
can ward off the plague.

18:20.590 --> 18:22.160
I hope it can help them.

18:22.160 --> 18:24.020
Xie, you are still so thoughtful.

18:25.200 --> 18:26.000
Then, Zheng,

18:26.550 --> 18:28.400
take the supplies and set off immediately.

18:28.400 --> 18:29.480
If there is any news,

18:29.480 --> 18:30.880
report back immediately.

18:30.880 --> 18:31.440
I

18:31.680 --> 18:32.350
obey.

18:32.510 --> 18:33.200
Wait.

18:33.960 --> 18:35.000
The situation in Huangpi Village

18:35.000 --> 18:36.750
may be more complex than we imagined.

18:36.750 --> 18:37.830
You must be careful

18:38.070 --> 18:40.000
and protect yourself and Xiao Chi.

18:40.030 --> 18:40.880
I understand.

18:41.750 --> 18:42.830
Please rest assured,

18:42.830 --> 18:44.630
Your Majesty and Your Highness.

18:44.680 --> 18:45.810
I will take my leave.

18:50.310 --> 18:53.000
Xie, you are the backbone of Jinglan.

18:53.350 --> 18:55.400
Then give me the throne.

18:55.480 --> 18:57.270
You can have it.

18:57.270 --> 18:59.030
Anyway, you won't treat me badly.

18:59.030 --> 19:01.070
I'd rather be an idle prince.

19:01.200 --> 19:02.460
You little clever one.

19:03.240 --> 19:04.240
The people of Jinglan

19:04.240 --> 19:05.350
and the glory of the Liu family,

19:05.350 --> 19:07.240
now rest on your shoulders.

19:07.590 --> 19:09.050
Even if you want to be idle,

19:09.270 --> 19:09.960
I,

19:09.960 --> 19:10.820
the officials,

19:10.830 --> 19:12.270
and our late father

19:12.270 --> 19:13.480
will not agree.

19:14.680 --> 19:18.160
You are carrying the whole country
of Jinglan on your shoulders.

19:18.160 --> 19:19.220
Do you understand?

19:19.750 --> 19:20.550
I understand.

19:42.550 --> 19:43.200
Cuizhi.

19:43.790 --> 19:44.590
Cuizhi.

19:44.750 --> 19:45.550
What's wrong?

19:46.000 --> 19:47.030
Physician Han,

19:47.030 --> 19:48.070
Physician Han, come quickly.

19:48.070 --> 19:49.670
My sister is vomiting blood.

19:51.030 --> 19:51.830
Help her up first.

19:51.830 --> 19:52.690
Physician Han.

19:52.790 --> 19:53.510
Come.

19:56.270 --> 19:57.110
Sit down.

19:58.240 --> 19:59.480
Go get some ginseng slices.

19:59.480 --> 20:00.070
Okay.

20:09.790 --> 20:11.920
How could there be signs of poisoning?

20:16.830 --> 20:17.400
Come on.

20:20.270 --> 20:21.600
Keep this in your mouth.

20:46.480 --> 20:47.790
How is my sister?

20:48.480 --> 20:49.880
She's fine for now.

20:50.270 --> 20:51.730
Thank you, Physician Han.

20:51.750 --> 20:53.950
We can never repay your great kindness.

20:55.830 --> 20:57.160
You stay here and take care of her.

20:57.160 --> 20:57.880
Okay.

21:06.830 --> 21:08.200
Why won't you let me out?

21:08.400 --> 21:10.000
We are short of
medicinal herbs in the village.

21:10.000 --> 21:11.750
I need to go out to buy medicinal herbs.

21:11.750 --> 21:12.550
Without an order,

21:12.550 --> 21:13.070
no one is allowed in or out.

21:13.070 --> 21:14.000
Physician Chen.

21:15.070 --> 21:16.030
What happened?

21:16.960 --> 21:17.760
General Xiao.

21:18.400 --> 21:20.400
The guards suddenly
stopped me from leaving today,

21:20.400 --> 21:21.270
saying the Death Plague

21:21.270 --> 21:24.530
in Huangpi Village is severe
and no one is allowed in or out.

21:24.920 --> 21:26.000
We don't have enough medicine now.

21:26.000 --> 21:27.270
Physician Chen needs
to go out to gather medicinal herbs.

21:27.270 --> 21:28.070
Besides,

21:28.070 --> 21:30.030
the situation in the village has improved.

21:30.030 --> 21:31.560
Who says it's that serious?

21:31.880 --> 21:33.200
This is an order from above.

21:33.200 --> 21:35.000
General Xiao, please
don't make it difficult for us.

21:35.000 --> 21:36.640
I know you're following orders,

21:36.640 --> 21:38.030
but we must get the medicine.

21:38.030 --> 21:38.830
Lord Xiao.

21:39.110 --> 21:41.270
We are acting on Lord Zhang's orders.

21:41.550 --> 21:44.030
Without an order,
no one is allowed in or out.

21:44.270 --> 21:45.510
Lord Zhang's orders?

21:46.070 --> 21:48.960
But this is a matter
of life and death for the villagers.

21:48.960 --> 21:51.160
Sorry, military orders must be obeyed.

21:51.160 --> 21:52.880
Fine. In that case,

21:53.070 --> 21:54.530
pardon me for being rough.

22:02.070 --> 22:02.880
Stop!

22:04.960 --> 22:05.750
Zheng?

22:09.790 --> 22:10.590
Lord Fei.

22:10.790 --> 22:12.750
We are ordered by Lord Zhang
to stand guard here.

22:12.750 --> 22:15.030
Without an order,
no one is allowed to leave the village.

22:15.030 --> 22:15.790
I am here

22:16.200 --> 22:17.550
by imperial decree.

22:17.960 --> 22:18.440
What?

22:19.440 --> 22:21.030
Does His Majesty

22:21.030 --> 22:22.830
have to listen to Lord Zhang now?

22:23.270 --> 22:24.200
I wouldn't dare.

22:26.750 --> 22:27.400
Chi,

22:27.720 --> 22:29.250
you've worked hard lately.

22:29.750 --> 22:31.440
How is the situation in the village now?

22:31.440 --> 22:34.000
The situation in the village
is much better now.

22:34.000 --> 22:35.510
Then these supplies and medicines...

22:35.510 --> 22:36.440
Put them inside.

22:36.550 --> 22:37.550
Thank you, Zheng.

22:38.350 --> 22:39.550
Listen up, everyone.

22:39.640 --> 22:42.070
Unload the supplies
and medicines from the carts

22:42.070 --> 22:43.070
and transport them into the village.

22:43.070 --> 22:44.030
Yes, Sir.

22:45.590 --> 22:46.400
Let's go.

23:01.830 --> 23:02.690
Physician Han.

23:07.640 --> 23:08.480
Lord Fei.

23:09.160 --> 23:10.200
Is Cuizhi's condition

23:10.200 --> 23:11.640
looking bad?

23:13.640 --> 23:15.240
Cuizhi's pulse

23:15.350 --> 23:16.810
shows signs of poisoning.

23:17.400 --> 23:18.200
Poisoning?

23:20.160 --> 23:21.420
How could this happen?

23:22.640 --> 23:23.440
Then is there

23:23.720 --> 23:25.050
any cure for the poison?

23:25.240 --> 23:26.640
There is a way,

23:26.880 --> 23:28.200
but the medicine is very strong.

23:28.200 --> 23:29.800
I have never tried it before.

23:31.030 --> 23:32.490
Physician Han, do you want

23:32.790 --> 23:34.520
to test the medicine on people?

23:36.750 --> 23:38.070
I need to confirm first

23:38.070 --> 23:40.270
if a healthy person
will be okay after taking this medicine.

23:40.270 --> 23:41.240
If they are fine,

23:41.240 --> 23:43.040
then I'll use it on the patients.

23:43.960 --> 23:44.880
Time is running out.

23:44.880 --> 23:46.880
I'll go prepare the medicine first.

23:52.200 --> 23:53.000
Xiao Chi,

23:53.590 --> 23:54.880
I'll return to the capital right now

23:54.880 --> 23:56.410
and find a death row inmate.

23:56.640 --> 23:57.640
I'm warning you,

23:58.480 --> 23:59.960
don't do anything stupid.

24:00.590 --> 24:02.030
Don't worry, Zheng.

24:02.440 --> 24:04.110
I'll be back as soon as possible.

24:04.110 --> 24:04.550
Okay.

24:14.160 --> 24:15.000
Physician Han.

24:15.000 --> 24:16.260
The medicine is ready.

24:16.270 --> 24:17.750
Why don't you test it on my sister?

24:17.750 --> 24:18.960
If anything happens,

24:18.960 --> 24:20.200
I won't blame anyone.

24:20.200 --> 24:21.440
Don't worry.

24:21.680 --> 24:23.080
This is the minimum dose.

24:23.400 --> 24:24.270
I need to find

24:24.270 --> 24:27.070
the right dosage for
both the healthy and the sick.

24:27.400 --> 24:29.000
Are you going to test it on yourself?

24:29.000 --> 24:30.030
Why are you here?

24:30.030 --> 24:31.430
Get out of here right now.

24:31.480 --> 24:32.640
If you're going to test the medicine,

24:32.640 --> 24:33.160
I...

24:33.160 --> 24:34.160
I didn't drink it.

24:35.350 --> 24:37.350
The whole village is
waiting for me to save them.

24:37.350 --> 24:39.080
I won't gamble with my own body.

24:40.880 --> 24:41.680
Really?

24:42.720 --> 24:43.070
Look.

24:43.480 --> 24:44.550
If I really drank it,

24:44.550 --> 24:46.030
how could I be completely fine?

24:46.030 --> 24:46.640
But...

24:46.640 --> 24:47.550
Alright.

24:48.160 --> 24:49.360
Wait for my good news.

24:58.640 --> 25:00.240
Jin Xi, turn around.

25:03.030 --> 25:04.090
You have a good eye.

25:04.550 --> 25:06.030
We chose it together.

25:19.550 --> 25:21.070
Is Lord Fei back?

25:21.070 --> 25:22.000
Not yet.

25:24.400 --> 25:25.480
Is the stuff ready?

25:25.480 --> 25:25.960
Mhm.

25:28.000 --> 25:28.730
Give it to me.

25:30.440 --> 25:31.440
What is this?

25:32.880 --> 25:35.000
Blood from my sister's fingertip.

25:36.200 --> 25:37.160
What is it for?

25:37.480 --> 25:38.110
Physician Han...

25:38.110 --> 25:38.880
Cuimiao.

25:40.000 --> 25:41.200
Physician Han wants
to use my sister's blood

25:41.200 --> 25:42.000
to get infected,

25:42.000 --> 25:43.830
and then continue testing the medicine.

25:43.830 --> 25:44.640
I'm leaving.

25:45.350 --> 25:46.680
Do you have a death wish?

25:49.790 --> 25:51.160
If I can use my life

25:51.270 --> 25:53.200
to save the whole Huangpi Village,

25:53.790 --> 25:54.680
it's worth it.

25:57.350 --> 25:59.480
If anyone should do it, it should be me.

26:00.240 --> 26:01.000
Xiao Chi!

26:03.270 --> 26:04.310
My body

26:04.830 --> 26:06.070
is already sick anyway.

26:06.070 --> 26:07.110
This way, you can find the cure faster.

26:07.110 --> 26:08.640
Xiao Chi, spit the blood out!

26:08.640 --> 26:09.590
Spit it out right now!

26:09.590 --> 26:10.510
Calm down.

26:10.510 --> 26:11.400
Listen to me.

26:11.790 --> 26:12.550
It has to be me

26:13.200 --> 26:14.270
who tests the medicine.

26:14.270 --> 26:15.310
But your body

26:15.310 --> 26:17.030
can't take any more torture.

26:17.030 --> 26:18.680
My body is already like this.

26:18.880 --> 26:21.000
It makes no difference
whether I test it or not.

26:21.000 --> 26:22.260
But you're different.

26:22.480 --> 26:24.340
You are everyone's only hope now.

26:24.350 --> 26:25.070
And,

26:26.790 --> 26:29.320
I don't want anything
to happen to you either.

26:39.640 --> 26:41.240
Then stay here tonight.

26:41.400 --> 26:42.460
Don't go anywhere.

26:42.680 --> 26:43.350
Okay.

26:44.830 --> 26:45.830
Lie down first.

26:47.480 --> 26:49.080
Is there a reaction already?

26:50.160 --> 26:50.960
It's fine.

26:51.350 --> 26:52.750
I just drank too fast.

26:52.750 --> 26:54.080
Just pour me a pot of tea.

26:54.880 --> 26:55.880
Go sit down first.

27:01.440 --> 27:02.840
I'll go pour you some tea.

27:10.480 --> 27:11.010
Cuimiao.

27:11.400 --> 27:11.830
Yes.

27:11.830 --> 27:13.590
Go bring General Xiao some tea.

27:13.680 --> 27:14.480
Okay.

27:28.270 --> 27:29.130
Physician Han.

27:29.310 --> 27:30.030
Physician Han.

27:30.030 --> 27:30.590
Physician Han!

27:30.590 --> 27:32.590
General Xiao threw up a lot of blood!

27:32.830 --> 27:33.790
Go find Physician Chen.

27:33.790 --> 27:34.400
Okay.

27:39.830 --> 27:40.640
I'm fine.

27:53.640 --> 27:54.720
Physician Han,

27:54.920 --> 27:57.200
General Xiao threw up so much black blood.

27:57.200 --> 27:58.440
Will he die?

27:59.200 --> 28:00.880
Don't talk nonsense, little girl.

28:00.880 --> 28:02.200
The general won't die.

28:02.510 --> 28:03.440
Physician Han,

28:03.680 --> 28:04.480
how is it?

28:07.880 --> 28:09.640
General Xiao has a high fever now.

28:09.640 --> 28:11.370
He is likely already infected.

28:11.960 --> 28:14.090
I want to try that prescription on him.

28:14.880 --> 28:16.880
But if we use the medicine rashly

28:17.000 --> 28:18.640
and something happens here,

28:18.640 --> 28:21.570
I'm afraid we won't be able
to bear the consequences.

28:21.960 --> 28:22.790
It's fine.

28:23.550 --> 28:24.410
I administered

28:24.550 --> 28:26.070
the poison to myself.

28:27.790 --> 28:29.050
Is the medicine ready?

28:29.750 --> 28:30.640
Bring it over.

28:33.790 --> 28:35.390
-Go get the medicine.
-Okay.

28:40.550 --> 28:41.680
I'm fine.

29:06.030 --> 29:06.830
General Xiao.

29:09.270 --> 29:10.160
I'm fine.

29:31.350 --> 29:32.790
How is that possible?

29:33.640 --> 29:36.000
I only used half the dosage.

29:39.790 --> 29:41.250
General Xiao's condition

29:41.440 --> 29:42.640
is not looking good.

29:43.350 --> 29:44.640
Plus he himself

29:44.640 --> 29:45.790
is naturally weak.

29:46.480 --> 29:48.440
If he can't make it through tonight,

29:48.440 --> 29:50.350
our lives are in danger.

29:51.960 --> 29:53.790
Actually, there is another way.

29:53.880 --> 29:54.830
Then treat him quickly.

29:54.830 --> 29:56.440
H-His condition can't wait.

29:56.440 --> 29:58.840
It's just that this acupuncture method...

29:59.270 --> 30:00.070
Xiao Chi.

30:01.400 --> 30:02.200
Xiao Chi.

30:02.960 --> 30:03.750
Xiao Chi.

30:07.270 --> 30:08.270
I'm fine.

30:08.830 --> 30:09.750
I'm fine.

30:10.200 --> 30:11.480
There's no time to lose.

30:11.480 --> 30:13.640
Physician Chen,
please undress General Xiao.
